<p>The Yamazaki Distillery in Shimamoto, Osaka, Japan is open 7 days week, with the exception of some special holidays. Guided tours are conducted 5 times a day, from 9:50 a.m. &ndash; 2:50 p.m. each day. The tour is approximately 80 minutes.</p>
<p>To take part in a guided tour, you can make a reservation online, or by calling the distillery. All availability is shown online. In the event that no slots are available at your desired time, we still encourage you to visit the Yamazaki Distillery and enjoy the on-site Whisky Museum&mdash;detailing the history of the House of Suntory and the Yamazaki Distillery&mdash; and the Tasting Counter (paid)&mdash;where you can taste many of our award-winning whiskies from the House of Suntory portfolio, as well as rare component whiskies only available at the distillery. Please also feel free to visit the Gift Shop!</p>
